    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned dual VANOS system. This chassis is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, offering a tactile shifting experience and linear power delivery to the rear-mounted variable M differential. The vehicle has undergone a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and a cooling system refresh to ensure long-term durability. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension kinematics remain sharp and the engine retains excellent compression across all cylinders. This is a driver-focused example, dialed in for peak performance and structural rigidity.",
