    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2019 Audi A6 Premium Plus is the perfect blend of performance and sophistication. Finished in a stunning Moonlight Blue Metallic, the exterior retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway driving. The 19-inch 10-spoke wheels are in excellent shape with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of Black Valcona leather and dark wood inlays; the seats remain firm and supportive, and the dual-screen MMI touch response system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this vehicle has been meticulously cared for with a full service history. The turbocharged engine pulls smoothly, the Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides confident handling in all weather, and the tires have approximately 70% tread remaining. It is a non-smoker vehicle, always garaged, and comes with two sets of keys and the original owner\u2019s manual. This car is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any immediate maintenance needs.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
