    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my car, and it's honestly been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-cared for over the years\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride that still looks great in the driveway! It drives smoothly and is all ready for its next big adventure. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how much fun it is to drive. Let me know if you have any questions!",
